The paper discusses electronic and remote voting, which involves security and cryptography (cs.CR), as well as the use of computer systems (cs.DS) and information theory (cs.IT). It also touches on software engineering (cs.SE) and cybernetics (cs.CY) in terms of the design and implementation of electronic voting systems.
